-try {
-  foo();
-} catch (err) {
-  throw new Error(err.message);
-}
-```
-
-**Valid examples:**
-
-```js
-try {
-  foo();
-} catch (err) {
-  throw new Error("fail", { cause: err });
-}
-```
-
-```js
-try {
-  foo();
-} catch (error) {
-  throw new Error("Something went wrong", { cause: error });
-}
-```
-
-**Valid example** when `requireCatchParameter` is `false`:
-
-Valid:
-
-```js
-try {
-  foo();
-} catch {
-  throw new Error("fail");
-}
-```
